                              "description":  "•  Transforming Studio Production: Helping production houses and studios slash production costs by 60-90% and accelerate timelines from weeks to days through AI-native filmmaking.\n•  Democratizing Cinematic Storytelling: Enabling storytellers to create studio-grade feature films, micro-dramas, and animations with unprecedented control over scene, character, and object consistency.\n• Building Next-Gen Video Tech: Leading the development of proprietary consistency engines and agentic AI workflows that solve the \"uncanny valley\" problem for long-form video content (\u003e10 mins)",
